**‘THE ENGINEER’ “Our engineers are the crux of operations here in the Alliance. Here’s your habitat suit. The life module is capable of sustaining you for six or seven years. It handles all your… inputs and outputs. Uh… Maybe grab yourself a nice meal before you suit up for the long haul? I dunno how you guys—“ “It is only sustenance. A fuel source...” “Uh… right… ahh… so you’ll also be issued one of these omni-repair tools. If you lose it you can locate it using your suit’s tracker. If it’s destroyed or your suit needs repair, contact your dispatcher ASAP. I believe we have you on stealth drone deployment? Have you been—“ “That’s correct. Thank you Lieutenant, you may open the bay doors. I’m ready.” “Y--you got it pal… Harvey! Open er up! 132 is real eager! …you sure you don’t need to tie up any loose ends? No final fair-wells? “Been waiting a long time for this, Lieutenant.”** - <@1076100303193112578> (fast)
